            <title>【教學+實試】Apple Intelligence 7 大實用功能　一鍵校對英文文法 + TLDR 長文總結 + 錄音即時轉文字</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-intelligence-7-functions</link>
