            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前發布了 iOS 及 iPadOS 18.1 Developer Beta 版本，是次更新亦推出了全新 AI 系統 Apple Intelligence。在 Apple Intelligence 人工智能加持下，Siri 將會更加好用，同時 Apple 亦加入了不少處理文字 AI 功能。有興趣搶先試玩的朋友可以看看小編稍早前和大家分享的教學（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/">教學連結</a>）。今日小編就會和大家看看，Apple Intelligence 有甚麼實用的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843-694x482.jpg" alt="Apple Intelligence" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>1. 電話即時錄音 + 轉文字、總結對話內容</h2><p>Apple Intelligence 亦加入了大家期待已久的電話錄音功能，可將來電者的説話生成文字稿，結束通話後可在備忘錄找到對話錄音及文字稿。除此之外 Apple Intelligence 設有「Summary」功能，能夠用 AI 總結對話內容，對於工作上時常要講電話的人來説，這個功能非常實用，可更有條理地紀錄和管理電話內容。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1.jpg 807w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲通話狀態時可以即時錄音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1254084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227-277x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="1213" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227-277x580.jpg 277w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227.jpg 381w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲通話結束後可在備忘錄找回錄音及文字稿</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1254085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1-302x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="1112" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1-302x580.jpg 302w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1.jpg 469w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple Intelligence 設有「Summary」功能，可幫用家總結對話內容</p><h2>2. 自由切換打字或語音召喚 Siri</h2><p>以往使用 Siri 時，僅能夠在打字和語音二者擇一，如果使用打字與 Siri 交流，需要在「輔助設定」選擇，每次切換都非常麻煩。升級至 Apple Intelligence 後，用家可以直接點擊螢幕底部的白色鍵，以文字呼喚 Siri，長按電源掣則可與 Siri 以語音對話，毋須再限定一種召喚 Siri 方式。語音召喚 Siri 時，Siri 亦從原來的球體變成框住 4 邊的光。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 可以用文字與 Siri 溝通</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以語音召喚 Siri 的話，iPad 的四邊則會發光</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安裝方法 + 申請教學</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">確保用戶掌握個人資料去向   Apple Intelligence 將提供詳細私隱報告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>3. 一鍵總結電郵</h2><p>大家工作時會收到各式各樣的電郵，有些電郵非常冗長，如果要全部讀完就會浪費很多時間和精神。升級至 Apple Intelligence 後，我們可以將讀電郵的工作交由 AI 完成，Apple Intelligence 可以幫我們總結電郵內容。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊綠框框住的 Summarize</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲隨即會在電郵上方顯示小總結</p><h2>4. 校對電郵</h2><p>除了總結電郵，Apple Intelligence 亦可幫用家校對，避免寄送文法有錯的電郵貽笑大方。打好電郵之後，長按螢幕直至浮現圖一所示選項，點擊「Writing Tools」即可選擇不同寫作工具。小編的回覆有明顯錯誤，現在就讓我們看看 Apple Intelligence 如何幫小編校對電郵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖一：選擇「Writing Tools」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖二：選擇「Proofread」</p><p>Apple Intelligence 會 highlight 有錯誤的地方並直接修正（紅色箭嘴示），綠色框可見目前正使用「Proofread」模式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖三：Apple Intelligence 會自動修正文法錯誤</p><h2>5. 改寫電郵</h2><p>Apple Intelligence 亦可幫用家利用不同的語氣改寫電郵。如校對一樣，打好電郵之後，長按螢幕直至浮現圖一所示選項，點擊「Writing Tools」即可選擇不同寫作工具。這次小編想 Apple Intelligence 幫我用專業的語氣改寫電郵內容，於是選擇了「Professional」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「Writing Tools」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖二：選擇「Professional」（綠色框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖三：Apple Intelligence 幫小編將內容改為專業的口吻（見紅框），綠框顯示目前正在使用「Professional」模式</p><h2>6. 語音備忘錄轉文字</h2><p>升級至 Apple Intelligence 後，Apple 加入了語音備忘錄轉文字功能，現在可以將錄音轉為逐字稿了，錄音時亦可即時同步顯示語音轉文字結果。小編覺得這個功能非常實用，出席記者會、觀看發布會時，可以錄音並直接轉為文字稿，方便之後進行編輯工作，不用再「默書」般邊聽錄音邊將句子打出來。小編實測過，利用錄音轉文字稿功能收聽 WWDC 2024，留意到其準確度算高，以後觀看發布會就方便得多了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錄音時可即時同步顯示語音轉文字結果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲錄音後亦可翻查文字稿，點擊右上角綠色框框住的按鈕</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可顯示逐字稿</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安裝方法 + 申請教學</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">確保用戶掌握個人資料去向   Apple Intelligence 將提供詳細私隱報告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>7. 總結長文</h2><p>小編每次看見長篇英文文章就會覺得頭痛，升級 Apple Intelligence 後，可以利用 AI 幫手「TLDR」以 4 種方式總結文章內容，分別是 Summary、Key Points、List 及 Table。首先 Highlight 你需要的文字，點擊「Writing Tools」，選擇所需的總結方式即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲highlight 所需文字後點擊「Writing Tools」（箭嘴示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按照個人需要選擇不同總結方式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Summary 會以一句句子總結選擇文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Key Points 以點列式總結選擇文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲List 同樣會以點列式總結選擇文字，但就較 Key Point 更加詳細</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Table 可利用表格總結選取文字，但小編覺得這個功能似乎尚未成熟，生成結果不太實用</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 120px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"><strong>總結類型</strong></td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>作用</strong></td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Summary</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以一句句子總結選擇文字</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Key Points</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以點列式總結選擇文字</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">List</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以點列式總結選擇文字，但比 Key Points 詳細一點</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Table</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以表格總結選擇文字<br />
（現階段不太穩定，不建議使用）</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>總結：功能實用　惟暫未支援中文</h2><p>小編實際試用過 6 種功能，覺得 Apple Intelligence 對工作上經常要處理文字的朋友非常好用，例如能夠幫大家整理文法、改寫電郵，亦可以「TLDR」快速摘要長篇文章內容，節省不少時間。作為記者，小編私心最喜歡的功能是錄音轉文字功能，絕對是出席記者會、發布會的好幫手，大大提升工作效率。惟一要扣分的位置是暫時仍未支援中文，希望 Apple 可以快點推出中文版 Apple Intelligence。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安裝方法 + 申請教學</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">確保用戶掌握個人資料去向   Apple Intelligence 將提供詳細私隱報告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/">【教學+實試】Apple Intelligence 7 大實用功能　一鍵校對英文文法 + TLDR 長文總結 + 錄音即時轉文字</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
